# Admin User Management Rule

Admin user management is a production operations console, not a simple profile CRUD page.

Required:
- KPI cards
- search/filter bar
- professional user table
- status badges
- plan/subscription badges
- role summary
- learning summary
- quota warning
- user detail drawer/page
- tabs: Overview, Learning, Plan & Quota, Roles & Permissions, Sessions, Support Notes, Audit
- confirmation + reason for sensitive actions
- audit log for sensitive actions

Forbidden:
- large inline create-user form as main content
- only showing name/email/locale
- only active status
- frontend-only permission checks
- hard-coded premium/free logic
- showing internal UUID/keycloak_id as normal UX
- destructive delete without soft-delete/anonymization flow